## 1. Executive Summary

This specification defines the comprehensive integration testing strategy for the VJLive3 backend wiring components. It establishes test scenarios, performance benchmarks, failure injection tests, and validation criteria to ensure the entire system works cohesively under real-world conditions.

**Critical Objectives:**
- Verify all wiring components work together end-to-end
- Validate 60 FPS sacred rail under load
- Test error recovery and graceful degradation
- Ensure memory stability over extended runs
- Verify agent→plugin communication at scale
- Validate telemetry accuracy and overhead
- Test configuration persistence and cloud sync
- Provide regression test suite for future development

